data.description: Spacious and move in ready 3 bedroom 2 bathroom Winter Park home on an oversized corner lot. Enjoy your gatherings on the large screened back porch. This house is centrally located to several of the main highways, Orlando Airport, downtown Orlando area, Park Avenue, Rollins College, UCF, restaurants and plenty of stores. Plumbing, electrical and water heater were all updated in 2019. Property features a spacious indoor laundry room with plenty of space for storage. Bathrooms have been remodeled. Backyard is completely fenced and large enough to keep an RV, trailer and more. Come check it out!
